.XI insert-file-name \- "\*(C0Insert filename into current buffer"
.SH NAME
insert-file-name \- Insert filename into current buffer
.Me $a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.na
.I n
\fBinsert-file-name\fR \*(C0
.ad
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B insert-file-name
inserts the current buffer's file name into the current buffer or, if entering
text on the  message  line then  enters  the file name into the  message  line
buffer.
.PP
If the numeric  argument \fIn\fR is \fC\-1\fR then the buffer name is inserted
into the buffer.
